%h1 You have logged out
%p You may <a href="/login">log in</a> again.

- if @url
  %p
    The application you have just logged out of has provided a link it would
    like you to follow.
  %p
    Please <a href="#{@url}" rel="nofollow">click here</a> to access
    <a href="#{@url}" rel="nofollow">#{@url}</a>.
